{{Quote|Tell her to meet us at the Next Chance.|Princess Leia Organa|<ref name="Shadows of the Empire (novel)">[[Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire (novel)|''Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire'' novel]]</ref>}}
The '''Next Chance''' was a hotel on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] and the [[Human replica droid]], [[Guri]] met there in the [[Standard year/Legends|year]] [[3 ABY/Legends|3.5 ABY]] to discuss plans of an alliance as Leia needed information on the attempted assassinations on [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker's]] life.

